+## Example Snippet
+
+```python
+class Engine:
+    def __init__(self, graph): self.graph = graph
+    def run(self, state):
+        node = self.graph.start
+        visited = set()
+        while node:
+            if node.id in visited: raise RuntimeError("cycle detected")
+            visited.add(node.id)
+            state = node.execute(state)
+            node = self.graph.next(node, state)
+        return state
+```
